---
title: Honey Ginger Prawns with stir-fried broccoli and jasmine rice
description: The Asian-inspired flavours in this prawn rice bowl take your mouth on a journey from sweet to heat. The ginger, honey, soy sauce, and garlic may be contrasting tastes but they definitely work together in this dish.
